About
Come tour Vegas's Best Kept Secret. Do you love Ford's or Chevy's? When you book a tour here at Nostalgia Street Rods, you’ll get access to a private collection of automobiles from 1910 to 1965. We also offer a large selection of memorabilia and antiques including signed sports memorabilia by Kobe Bryant, NFL Football Teams, Arnold Palmer and many more. Music memorabilia signed by musicians like Elvis Presley, Jimmy Hendrix, The Rolling Stones and much more! If you love hot rods and other classic cars, you’ll absolutely love it here at Nostalgia Street Rods.
Duration: 1-2 hours

Jun 2023 • Couples
Truly great collection, incredibly knowledgeable tour guide and an absolute gem of a seemingly secret, hidden vegas treasure. I'm not sure they promote the place as well as they could and we had no idea it was so extensive and varied.
